# SECURITY-04: HTTP Security Headers (for Netlify / static hosting)
/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-eval'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data:; font-src 'self'; media-src 'self'; connect-src 'self' https://texttospeech.googleapis.com https://eastus.tts.speech.microsoft.com
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
